mq r8 rdata-value
mq value-site r9
mq r9 rdata-value-site

lq hash-data-name rdi
lq rdata-key rsi
mq equations r12
mq views r13
mq vects r11
addc vects av r11
dct r11

add 10000 rsp
ret

